sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as React UI
  participant API as ResourceLibrary.API
  participant CQ as MediatR CQRS
  participant SVC as AiAudioService
  participant DEM as Demucs

  UI->>API: POST /api/aiAudio/separate?stems=4 (multipart: file)
  API->>CQ: SeparateAudioCommand
  CQ->>SVC: SeparateAsync(stream, stems)
  SVC->>DEM: POST /separate?stems=4
  DEM-->>SVC: application/zip (stems.zip)
  SVC-->>CQ: byte[]
  CQ-->>API: byte[] (zip)
  API-->>UI: File(stems.zip)
